## Notes: |cFFFF0000Version 2.3.2|r - SKEM Edition. |n|n|cffffffffNew in v2.3.2:|r|n- Added a built-in Settings tab with better tab sizing and UI scale relayout fixes|n- Embedded full Roll History in the main window with mouse-wheel scrolling|n- Added Use My Gold and trade-based wager tracking modes|n- Fixed History tab scrollbar refresh and roll history leaking across tabs|n- Roll odds now show from your perspective (win after your roll, loss after theirs)|n|n|cffffffffCore Features:|r|n- Whisper-based challenge notifications between addon users|n- Edit and delete individual game records|n- Gold tracking with /dr fixgold repair command|n- Intuitive AceGUI-based interface|n- Detailed win/loss history tracking per player|n- Advanced gold tracking with streaks and statistics|n- Smart minimap integration with LibDBIcon|n- Cross-version compatibility (Classic Era, TBC, Wrath, Cata, Retail)|n|n|cffffffffCommands:|r|n- |cffffff00/dr or /deathroll:|r Open the main DeathRoll window|n- |cff00ff00/dr config:|r Open configuration options|n- |cff82c5ff/dr accept:|r Accept a pending challenge|n- |cff82c5ff/dr decline:|r Decline a pending challenge|n- |cff82c5ff/dr edit:|r Edit recent game records|n- |cff82c5ff/dr fixgold:|r Recalculate gold tracking totals|n- |cff82c5ff/dr size:|r Show current window size|n- |cff82c5ff/drh [player]:|r View history with specific player|n|n|cffbbbbbbBy 0xTrk - Powered by Ace3|r
